      "code": "struct DetailScreen: View {\n    var body: some View {\n        content.task {            // tied to the view's lifetime (b3-05)\n            await vm.load()       // → gRPC call, 5s deadline\n        }\n    }\n}\n// user swipes away at t = 0.1s. Then what?",
